<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Tu viens de soumettre ton feedback.</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
    <style>
        .email-background {
            background: #eee;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .email-container,
        .pre-header,
        .footer {
            max-width: 500px;
            background: #dddbf8;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            margin: 0px auto;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .pre-header {
            background: #eee;
            color: #eee;
            font-size: 5px;
        }

        img {
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        h1,
        h2 {
            margin: 10px 30px;
        }

        p {
            margin: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #222324;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .confirm-email {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            background: #6558f5;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            background: none;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer,
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #222324;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-background" style="background: #eee; padding: 10px">
        <div class="pre-header" style="
          max-width: 500px;
          background: #eee;
          font-family: sans-serif;
          margin: 0px auto;
          overflow: hidden;
          border-radius: 5px;
          color: #eee;
          font-size: 5px;
        ">
            Tu viens à l'instant de recevoir un feedback sur Feedward.
            L'application qui te permet d'évaluer ton équipe mangériale en toute
            sérénité.
        </div>
        <div class="email-container" style="
          max-width: 500px;
          background: #dddbf8;
          font-family: sans-serif;
          margin: 0px auto;
          overflow: hidden;
          border-radius: 5px;
        ">
            <h3 style="margin: 10px 30px">Tu as recu un feedback !</h3>
            <h4 style="margin: 10px 30px">
                Tu viens de recevoir un feedback sur Feedward !
            </h4>
            <img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/izxswKdmqmQrS/source.gif" alt="Bravo!" style="max-width: 100%" />
            <p style="
            margin: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #222324;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-weight: 300;
          ">
                Tu peux le retrouver dans ton dashboard.<br />
            </p>
            <div class="confirm-email" style="
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            background: #6558f5;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 20px;
          ">
                <%= link_to "Accède à ton dashboard", dashboard_url %><br />
            </div>

            <p style="
            margin: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #222324;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-weight: 300;
          ">
                Merci pour ta confiance.
            </p>
            <p style="
            margin: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #222324;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-weight: 300;
          ">
                À très vite sur Feedward !
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer" style="
          max-width: 500px;
          background: none;
          font-family: sans-serif;
          margin: 0px auto;
          overflow: hidden;
          border-radius: 5px;
          text-align: center;
          padding: 20px;
          font-size: 14px;
          text-decoration: none;
          color: #222324;
        ">
            <a href="http://getfeedward.com/" style="text-decoration: none; color: #222324">Visiter le site</a>
            |
            <a href="mailto:contact@getfeedward.com" style="text-decoration: none; color: #222324">Nous contacter</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>